Place the files

sqlite3.h
sqlite3.c

from an SQLCipher amalgamation of your choice here. See, for instance,
    https://downloads.leap.se/libs/pysqlcipher/amalgamation-sqlcipher-2.1.0.zip

Or you create the amalgamation from the current source at
    https://github.com/sqlcipher/sqlcipher
by running
    ./configure
    make .target_source
    tclsh tool/mksqlite3c.tcl